narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Mathematical Analysis. Learned applications of Brownian motion, Heat kernel, etc. Developed an understanding of how mathematical analysis can be useful in the physical context.
I developed knowledge/skills into Brownian motion, eigenfunction and harmonic extension and so on.
